|  ![kolor4](/assets/klany/color4.png)  |       brak       |                   brak                    | 
|  ![kolor5](/assets/klany/color5.png)  |       brak       |                   brak                    |
|  ![kolor6](/assets/klany/color6.png)  | 20000 kokscoinow |                   brak                    |
